{"tid":220314,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"肥真係原罪，死左都要累人累物","createTime":"2017-04-28T00:45:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-28T00:49:23.000Z","uid":32051,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8085a06f7b8a502f422644f1245e7590b0164240","tid":220314,"uid":32051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T00:45:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">癡肥遺體脂肪太多 火化時令火勢變猛釀火災</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n美國俄亥俄州一間殯儀館發生離奇意外，職員火化一具癡肥遺體時，火勢突然變猛，更擴散至火化爐外釀成火警；幸事件中無人受傷，火勢亦未波及其他屍體。<br />\n<br />\n大火發生在周二晚，殯儀館負責人卡奇恩（Don Catchen）指，火化期間火勢變得強勁，令大火擴散至火化爐外，並燒著一個火化箱，「那具遺體屬癡肥，火化過程明顯比一般的更熱」。<br />\n<br />\n消防員表示幸火葬場做足防火措施，成功阻止火勢蔓延，事件沒人受傷，亦未有波及其他屍體。<br />\n<br />\n業內人士指火化癡肥遺體有危險，是因為會出現俗稱「油脂火」，維珍尼亞州2014年火化一具500磅遺體時亦曾發生火警；奧地利在2012年火化一具440磅的女屍時亦引發火燭，令消防員「覆蓋着一層烏黑油脂」。<br />\n<br />\n英國《都巿報》/《每日鏡報》<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nSource <a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170428&amp;guid=56621060&amp;category_guid=10793140&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170428%26guid%3D56621060%26category_guid%3D10793140%26category%3Dinstant&d=ulKCtXgG4rwmRR8qyGKIuf755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=711d315a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170428%26guid%3D56621060%26category_guid%3D10793140%26category%3Dinstant&h=ddaf42cc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170428&amp;guid=56621060&amp;category_guid=10793140&amp;category=instant</a>"},{"pid":"0957a8f9f8083b965e814ec8d8ba747c751ef7fe","tid":220314,"uid":32051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T00:47:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170427/large/1493285949_bfcf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170427%2Flarge%2F1493285949_bfcf.jpg&h=bd52b2e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170427/large/1493286431_86d4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170427%2Flarge%2F1493286431_86d4.jpg&h=073d9729&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170427/large/1493286433_df7c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170427%2Flarge%2F1493286433_df7c.jpg&h=b8ed6ca5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f1455cf1553169e9e702058781bb15d2ca62f074","tid":220314,"uid":863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T00:49:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}